75
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:15,300
Observe attentivement lorsque tu peins.

76
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:21,700
D'accord.

77
00:06:21,700 --> 00:06:23,400
Machisu,

78
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:26,400
